376	14	Amazon Prime Day kitchen deals: It's the last day to get up to 50 percent off air fryers, Instant Pots, blenders and more	https://www.engadget.com/deals/amazon-prime-day-kitchen-deals-its-the-last-day-to-get-up-to-50-percent-off-air-fryers-instant-pots-blenders-and-more-180019300.html?src=rss	<p>In cooking, timing is critical. So maybe you're just waiting until the right moment before you sauce up your kitchen game with discounts on new gear. That time is now. <a href="https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-the-last-day-our-top-picks-on-headphones-tvs-robot-vacuums-and-more-120028336.html">Amazon's Prime Day sale </a>is nearly over (it ends at midnight, Pacific time) but there are still quite a few deals on kitchen tech that we think are worth your while. After all, Engadget has been reviewing kitchen gadgets for years and we have our opinions. Everything here is from brands and models we tested in our own kitchens — and we linked to our reviews so you can read more. Here are the best <a href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/">Prime Day</a> kitchen deals we could find.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><strong><em>Editor's note</em></strong><em>: We've waited the entire Prime Day event to see if </em><a href="https://www.engadget.com/ninja-creami-review-this-machine-makes-your-frozen-dreams-come-true-143155174.html"><em>Ninja's Creami ice cream maker</em></a><em> would see a good discount, and it never really materialized. Right now, a </em><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BLGR5JPV&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=bundle&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQihpVdnVgKsPjAjwXVeCrBCbIQFRFwpRtIyMY_8i52y&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNinja-NC301-CREAMi-Containers-Bundle%2Fdp%2FB0BLGR5JPV"><em>bundle</em></a><em> with extra containers is selling for $200, but that's still well above the low of $160 we saw as recently as January. </em></p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-air-fryer-deals">Prime Day air fryer deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0B15Q3HCQ&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Ninja+Foodie+Dual+Zone+Air+Fryer+%2810+QT%29+for+%24160+%28%2470+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbRjQvgVrlMnQ7-As93GT_KxZd4CbP3dbde6i6thWAiI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B15Q3HCQ"><strong>Ninja Foodie Dual Zone Air Fryer (10 QT) for $160 ($70 off)</strong></a>: This is the air fryer to pick if you’ve ever wished you could air fry two different things at the same time. We named it the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-air-fryers-133047180.html#:~:text=Ninja-,Best%20dual%2Dzone%20air%20fryer,-Ninja%20DZ401%20Foodi">best dual-zone air fryer</a> you can get — it even has a feature that makes sure the two different foods are ready at the same time. This $160 price tag is the lowest price we've seen since Black Friday last year.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B08R6KMBQT&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Instant+Pot+Vortex+Plus+Air+Fryer+%284QT%29+for+%2465+%2850+percent+off+with+Prime%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOFI2S01CUVQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOFI2S01CUVQiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATyYlam_pwhbToMcEQC98bhqjphNiHo5stwsJZgR1j21&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08R6KMBQT"><strong>Instant Pot Vortex Plus Air Fryer (4QT) for $65 (50 percent off with Prime)</strong></a>: Here’s a smaller version of the Instant air fryer we named best overall. It has a four-quart capacity, which is perfect for one person and small kitchens. And, like its larger sibling, pre-heats quickly.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0C33CHG99&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Cosori+Air+Fryer+9-in-1+for+%2490+%28%2430+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzMzQ0hHOTk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzMzQ0hHOTkiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARP1axn-nLRzkH_z5mQ11RlA0odlzerrz3TGKTm-z6Ex&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C33CHG99"><strong>Cosori Air Fryer 9-in-1 for $90 ($30 off)</strong></a>: The <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-air-fryers-133047180.html#:~:text=overall%20%2D%20runner%20up-,Cosori%206%2Dquart%209%2Din%2D1%20air%20fryer,-Capacity%3A%206">runner up pick</a> in our air fryer guide has a spacious cooking capacity yet takes up surprisingly little counter space. Little features like an intuitive touchscreen, a safety release button on the basket and an auto-pause feature set this cooker apart.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B01N5UPTZS&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Breville+Smart+Oven+Air+Fryer+Pro+for+%24320+%28%2480+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQ_xha7NbVaH8GjdeMRWgehMHhDBovxoyiDGp3-ufNmL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB01N5UPTZS"><strong>Breville Smart Oven Air Fryer Pro for $320 ($80 off)</strong></a>: This is the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-air-fryers-133047180.html#:~:text=fryer%20toaster%20oven-,Breville%20Smart%20Oven%20Air%20Fryer%20Pro,-Capacity%3A%201">premium pick</a> in our air fryer guide — but really, it does far more than just air fry. As our reviewer noted, its massive cubic-foot-capacity and numerous cook modes make this more like an auxiliary oven. (It can even cook an entire 14-pound turkey.) It went on sale for $300 during last year's Black Friday sales.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B07FDJMC9Q&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Ninja+Air+Fryer+%284+QT%29+for+%2480+%28%2450+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYA434My0cPdvXzvlChEQ1cdzNKhDJgwNs-pZwUmae3d&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNinja-AF101-Fryer-Black-gray%2Fdp%2FB07FDJMC9Q"><strong>Ninja Air Fryer (4 QT) for $80 ($50 off)</strong></a>: The <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-air-fryers-133047180.html#:~:text=Instant%20Pot-,Best%20budget%20air%20fryer,-Instant%20Pot%20Vortex">budget pick</a> from our air fryer guide isn’t currently on sale, but this four-quart Ninja fryer has twice the capacity and is nearly the same price. It can also roast and dehydrate in addition to air frying and reheating.</p> \n<p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-air-fryers-133047180.html#best-air-fryer-accessories"><strong>Check out our guide to air fryers to read our testing results.</strong></a></p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-instant-pot-and-rice-cooker-deals">Prime Day Instant Pot and rice cooker deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B087H24T6G&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Cuckoo+Twin+Pressure+Rice+Cooker+for+%24190+%28%2470+off+with+Prime%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwODdIMjRUNkc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwODdIMjRUNkciLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAT9lJTuTMPkD6ME4JI7WdjeyL0bf7__p-3fLjkSllLqy&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB087H24T6G"><strong>Cuckoo Twin Pressure Rice Cooker for $190 ($70 off with Prime)</strong></a>: This is the best premium rice cooker <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-rice-cooker-120015478.html">in our guide</a> to those machines. We like how quickly it cooks all types of rice to perfection (we tested it with long-grain white basmati, brown and sushi-grade white rice). Just keep in mind that it can be a little difficult to clean and the manual isn’t the most user-friendly.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0752VWV65&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Hamilton+Beach+Digital+Programmable+Rice+Cooker+for+%2440+%28%2410+off+with+Prime%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwNzUyVldWNjU_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwNzUyVldWNjUiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdAN9soXGRjYaNihZEB1oSObO31QFwdkXPSttyh--CbV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0752VWV65"><strong>Hamilton Beach Digital Programmable Rice Cooker for $40 ($10 off with Prime)</strong></a>: Our top pick for a budget rice cooker is on sale for Prime members. The brown rice came out particularly good<a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-rice-cooker-120015478.html"> in our tests</a> and the cooker is easy to clean with a dishwasher-safe cooker pot and steamer basket. Just note that it’s pretty small and doesn’t have the granular controls of pricer models.</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-kitchen-tech-deals">Prime Day kitchen tech deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0de15002-ec35-49d8-b24c-3d060213cd2b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Ooni+Pizza+Ovens&amp;linkText=Ooni+Volt+12+Electric+Indoor+Pizza+Oven+for+%24630+%28%24270+off%29+from+Ooni&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL29vbmkuY29tL3Byb2R1Y3RzL29vbmktdm9sdCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL29vbmkuY29tL3Byb2R1Y3RzL29vbmktdm9sdCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAU4z8tquT4Lqo9CjJoUuEEJtyPNlWKfaXajeyhlcrSJU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fooni.com%2Fproducts%2Fooni-volt"><strong>Ooni Volt 12 Electric Indoor Pizza Oven for $630 ($270 off) from Ooni</strong></a>: <em>Note: This deal has </em><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0C62HWZPQ&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=expired+at+Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZBDZpZzeu3Q0Whed4QsTo8kxRgcexSdKitw28sEPBAG&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0C62HWZPQ"><em>expired at Amazon</em></a><em>, but is still available </em><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0de15002-ec35-49d8-b24c-3d060213cd2b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Ooni+Pizza+Ovens&amp;linkText=directly+from+Ooni&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL29vbmkuY29tL3Byb2R1Y3RzL29vbmktdm9sdCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL29vbmkuY29tL3Byb2R1Y3RzL29vbmktdm9sdCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAU4z8tquT4Lqo9CjJoUuEEJtyPNlWKfaXajeyhlcrSJU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fooni.com%2Fproducts%2Fooni-volt"><em>directly from Ooni</em></a><em>.</em> The Volt 12 is our pick for the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-pizza-oven-141550352.html#:~:text=Billy%20Steele%20/%20Engadget-,Best%20indoor%20pizza%20oven,-Ooni%20Volt%2012">best indoor pizza oven</a> — but it can be used outdoors as well thanks to its weather-resistant design. It has front-mounted controls that let you individually control the upper and lower heating elements and it can get up to 850 degrees Fahrenheit in as little as 20 minutes.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BLGR5JPV&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Ninja+CREAMi+Ice+Cream+Maker+%28bundle%29+for+%24200+%28%2430+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQihpVdnVgKsPjAjwXVeCrBCbIQFRFwpRtIyMY_8i52y&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNinja-NC301-CREAMi-Containers-Bundle%2Fdp%2FB0BLGR5JPV"><strong>Ninja CREAMi Ice Cream Maker (bundle) for $200 ($30 off)</strong></a>: We said this machine “<a href="https://www.engadget.com/ninja-creami-review-this-machine-makes-your-frozen-dreams-come-true-143155174.html">makes your frozen dreams come true</a>.” It’s easy to use and makes thick, dense ice cream with flavors that are more intense and textures that are smoother than rival ice cream makers. Plus most of the parts are machine washable or easily rinsed. This bundle comes with extra containers and is the lowest price we’ve seen in a few months, but note that the Creami sold for $160 as recently as January.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0C384T4P2&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Breville+Joule+Turbo+Sous+Vide+Machine+for+%24200+%28%2450+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzM4NFQ0UDI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzM4NFQ0UDIiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATnUgzKek_ZpudOlwKPOe1bfb9P-1jKNrE70XJwSCL85&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C384T4P2"><strong>Breville Joule Turbo Sous Vide Machine for $200 ($50 off)</strong></a>: The <a href="https://www.engadget.com/best-sous-vide-133025288.html">premium pick</a> in our guide to sous vice machines has a powerful 1,100-watt heater that cuts down on cooking times. It also uses your phone as the controller (just don’t get it if you’re hoping for on-device buttons).</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BQ9F56WV&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Anova+Sous+Vide+Cooker+3.0+for+%24138+%2840+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYBMhzTpcratgaf3h-i-HCa-N45Z1GnV7c7Tjlv0gIq5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BQ9F56WV"><strong>Anova Sous Vide Cooker 3.0 for $138 (40 percent off)</strong></a>: Our top pick for a <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-sous-vide-133025288.html">sous vide machine</a> delivers 1,100 watts of power and a flow rate of eight liters per minute which will get your water up to the right temperature faster. It also has intuitive digital touch controls and Wi-Fi connectivity.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B003R28HWQ&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Breville+Juice+Fountain+Plus+for+%24120+%28%2460+off+with+Prime%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwMDNSMjhIV1E_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwMDNSMjhIV1EiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARuUZZSGJmq-TZCJU399ql1VIEv2_6p1_juHzusZOTzT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB003R28HWQ"><strong>Breville Juice Fountain Plus for $120 ($60 off with Prime)</strong></a>: The extraction abilities on this machine are <a href="https://www.engadget.com/breville-juice-fountain-plus-irl-150059913.html">impressive</a>. Plus we found it relatively easy to clean (as long as you do it right after you juice). It takes up a good amount of space, but can extract an impressive amount of juice from even the driest-seeming carrot. This is the lowest price in a while, but it went down to $110 in January.</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-kitchenaid-and-blender-deals">Prime Day KitchenAid and blender deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B003OXNBYC&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=KitchenAid+Classic+Series+%284.5+QT%29+for+%24300+%28%2450+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwMDNPWE5CWUM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwMDNPWE5CWUMiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYL_aoTC_5c2ZK4e4PBEDWU-tv_PYiUe-_-dW6v3teKo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB003OXNBYC"><strong>KitchenAid Classic Series (4.5 QT) for $300 ($50 off)</strong></a>: Prime Day and Black Friday sales are usually the best times to snag Kitchen Aid’s iconic mixers — unfortunately, this discount isn’t even as good as the $250 it sold for in May. Still you can save $50 on a classic appliance that we recommend in our guide to<a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-kitchen-tech-gadgets-small-appliances-124515179.html"> essential kitchen gadgets</a>. These mixers are durable, reliable and, with the wide range of attachments, can truly expand your cooking arsenal.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B008H4SLV6&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Vitamix+5200+Blender+Professional-Grade+for+%24350+%28%24150+off+with+Prime%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwMDhINFNMVjY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwMDhINFNMVjYiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXh7xCJ2CnB985xKw7GoSCurH8zTcMcyGSeuFm5uq4TR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB008H4SLV6"><strong>Vitamix 5200 Blender Professional-Grade for $350 ($150 off with Prime)</strong></a>: I can personally attest to the nearly magical abilities of Vitamix blenders. It can make chunky salsas, smooth-as-silk soups and smoothies in which the chia and hemp seeds seem to disappear into the fruit. This pro-grade model is down to the lowest price we’ve tracked this year.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B08F2SS6T2&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=KitchenAid+Variable+Speed+Corded+Hand+Blender+for+%2455+%28%2415+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOEYyU1M2VDI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwOEYyU1M2VDIiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXFTI6R253j4vtumh0kWNYui42UqF8b7hmDEJeQbb_D2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08F2SS6T2"><strong>KitchenAid Variable Speed Corded Hand Blender for $55 ($15 off)</strong></a>: We recommend the cordless version of this immersion blender<a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-immersion-blenders-150006296.html"> in our guide</a> to those appliances. This corded version has the same variable speed trigger which makes it easy to control your recipes. Note that this sold for $5 less as recently as May.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B07GC9XZ9W&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Vitamix+E310+Explorian+Blender+for+%24330+%28%2450+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwN0dDOVhaOVc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNWE5YWVlZDYtZGMwYi00OTgxLWEyMmEtYmU2MmZhZjJhZDkwIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwN0dDOVhaOVciLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYvmzvZozaWR0SXGD4_DT332GhMC-DkNOMHc7DWBnuKd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07GC9XZ9W"><strong>Vitamix E310 Explorian Blender for $330 ($50 off)</strong></a>: Note that we've seen this go for as little as $255 in past sales, and it dropped to $300 as recently as May. But this is still a decent $50 discount on a blender that will make any food you put in it smooth. We recommend it in our guide to the best<a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-kitchen-tech-gadgets-small-appliances-124515179.html"> kitchen tech</a>.</p> \n<h3 id="jump-link-expired-deals">Expired deals</h3> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BF7HJ8MX&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Fellow+Stagg+EKG+Pro+electric+kettle+for+%24160+%28%2435+off+with+Prime%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0ZlbGxvdy1FbGVjdHJpYy1Qb3VyLW92ZXItVGVtcGVyYXR1cmUtU3RvcHdhdGNoL2RwL0IwQkY3SEo4TVg_&amp;signature=AQAAAQ3fv7KPqmazV_7a9YRq6V4YNNRCnKKNzk01ZgPx6SKf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFellow-Electric-Pour-over-Temperature-Stopwatch%2Fdp%2FB0BF7HJ8MX"><del><strong>Fellow Stagg EKG Pro electric kettle for $160 ($35 off with Prime)</strong></del></a><del>: This exquisitely designed kettle has an LCD panel built into the base so you can choose a specific temperature down to the degree. And the hold feature keeps water hot for up to an hour. I bought this after reading our</del><a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-gifts-to-buy-tea-lovers-140022326.html"><del> tea guide</del></a><del> and have appreciated the steady pour every morning since. You’ll likely only see the sale price if you’re a Prime member.</del></p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B09T7BWJNP&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Mannkitchen+Pepper+Cannon+for+%24160+%28%2440+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVEzPyyrMV50FXcnsergz-NhUxoBbuTS5PoD6ati9Jiv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMANNKITCHEN-Pepper-Cannon-Professional-Output%2Fdp%2FB09T7BWJNP"><del><strong>Mannkitchen Pepper Cannon for $160 ($40 off)</strong></del></a><del>: Not everyone needs a super expensive pepper mill. But it nonetheless became one of our reviewer’s </del><a href="https://www.engadget.com/mannkitchen-pepper-cannon-irl-153031695.html"><del>favorite pieces of kitchen gear</del></a><del>. A side-by-side comparison showed us just how much more pepper came out of the cannon compared to a standard store-bought mill.</del></p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Instant+Pot+Duo+Plus+9-in-1+%286+QT%29+for+%2470+%28%2470+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbm8lFYiocrCWgDjDOO2L6_cX3GM8MGlhbELLEziPldz&amp;gcReferrer=http%3A%2F%2Famazon.com%2Fdp%2FB01NBKTPTS"><del><strong>Instant Pot Duo Plus 9-in-1 (6 QT) for $70 ($70 off)</strong></del></a><del>: Perhaps you know someone who has somehow gotten this far in life without owning an Instant Pot — perhaps that someone is you. Amazon’s Prime Day is a golden opportunity to remedy that. We named it the </del><a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-kitchen-tech-gadgets-small-appliances-124515179.html"><del>best multi-cooker you can buy</del></a><del> in our guide to kitchen tech.</del></p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B096N28SZP&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5a9aeed6-dc0b-4981-a22a-be62faf2ad90&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Instant+Vortex+Plus+Air+Fryer+%286+QT%29+for+%24100+%28%2470+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZniLD0PwfhSU_g2HX0a7YkF96RTmylxGJFGQxUUghVT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB096N28SZP"><del><strong>Instant Vortex Plus Air Fryer (6 QT) for $100 ($70 off)</strong></del></a><del>: After studious testing (and dutiful eating) our reviewers named this one the</del><a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/kitchen-tech/best-air-fryers-133047180.html#:~:text=Instant%20Pot-,Best%20air%20fryer%20overall,-Instant%20Vortex%20Plus"><del> best air fryer you can buy</del></a><del>. And, after reading that assessment, I bought one myself so I can verify this is one great machine. The Odor Ease tech really does keep the cooking smells at bay and the window lets me keep an eye on all the crisping that’s going on in there.</del></p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/deals/amazon-prime-day-kitchen-deals-its-the-last-day-to-get-up-to-50-percent-off-air-fryers-instant-pots-blenders-and-more-180019300.html?src=rss	2025-07-11 23:45:35	Amy Skorheim	f	2025-07-14 05:01:46.484518
377	14	Prime Day 2025: The best headphone and earbud deals from Sony, Beats, Bose and more for the last day of the sale	https://www.engadget.com/deals/prime-day-2025-the-best-headphone-and-earbud-deals-from-sony-beats-bose-and-more-for-the-last-day-of-the-sale-082347142.html?src=rss	<p>Time is almost up on <a href="https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-the-last-day-our-top-picks-on-headphones-tvs-robot-vacuums-and-more-120028336.html">Prime Day</a>, so don't miss your chance at some of the best headphone and earbud deals of the year. There are still great options available from a lot of big names, and since we’ve reviewed nearly the entire list, we know what the best choices are during Amazon’s annual sale days. So, put our expertise to good use before it’s too late and let us guide you through the best Prime Day deals on still left to get on headphones and earbuds. Time is short, so don’t waste it trying to figure out meaningful features on your own. All of the deals below are still available late on day 4, but time is running out if you still want to take advantage of these discounts.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-sony-deals">Prime Day Sony deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0F3PQHWTZ&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Sony+WH-1000XM6+headphones+for+%24428+%28%2422+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1NvbnktV0gtMTAwMFhNNi1IZWFkcGhvbmVzLU1pY3JvcGhvbmVzLVN0dWRpby1RdWFsaXR5L2RwL0IwRjNQUUhXVFo_&amp;signature=AQAAAX5uj6Pc1w1iJKb0mux2oK0w1E5HrEUOkqtkKmOdih8Z&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-WH-1000XM6-Headphones-Microphones-Studio-Quality%2Fdp%2FB0F3PQHWTZ"><strong>Sony WH-1000XM6 headphones for $428 ($22 off):</strong></a> Sony's latest flagship headphones have only been out a few months and we're already seeing a small discount on them. These are my top pick in our headphones guide for the combination of advanced features, comfy fit, great sound and improved active noise cancellation (ANC).&nbsp;</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CWVXTK6Z&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Sony+ULT+Wear+headphones+for+%24128+%28%2472+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1NvbnktQ2FuY2VsaW5nLVdpcmVsZXNzLUhlYWRwaG9uZXMtQ29tZm9ydGFibGUvZHAvQjBDV1ZYVEs2Wi8_&amp;signature=AQAAAVYVkgRne1z0XQlAEUYawbe_pzSldXPUIJOJ8sR34t8W&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Canceling-Wireless-Headphones-Comfortable%2Fdp%2FB0CWVXTK6Z%2F"><strong>Sony ULT Wear headphones for $128 ($72 off):</strong></a> If you're after a solid set of Sony cans but don't want to splurge for the 1000X line, the ULT Wear is a good option. There are a bunch of handy features and robust sound with ULT bass boost.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BS1QCFHX&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Sony+WH-CH720N+headphones+for+%2478+%28%2472+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1NvbnktV0gtQ0g3MjBOLUNhbmNlbGluZy1IZWFkcGhvbmVzLU1pY3JvcGhvbmUvZHAvQjBCUzFRQ0ZIWC8_&amp;signature=AQAAAQEWrV7OLIN-KRuzPlfrdDBibScrBtTdEB8P-vvKLBxJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-WH-CH720N-Canceling-Headphones-Microphone%2Fdp%2FB0BS1QCFHX%2F"><strong>Sony WH-CH720N headphones for $78 ($72 off):</strong></a> The cheapest Sony headphones we'd recommend for Prime Day are no slouch. They're lightweight and comfy with respectable sound for the price. You also get Adaptive Sound Control, 360 Reality Audio and multipoint Bluetooth on this budget model.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0C33XXS56&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Sony+WF-1000XM5+earbuds+for+%24198+%28%24102+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzMzWFhTNTY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmU3MWJjYjUtZTIwMC00MWMyLWEzMTUtZTY4MjM5NDRlMjc2Iiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzMzWFhTNTYiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcxEVyyy3onVP6vj6rt2whZHaqvjo50iHFEywV8sOZqw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C33XXS56"><strong>Sony WF-1000XM5 earbuds for $198 ($102 off):</strong></a> My top pick for best earbuds is also on sale for Prime Day. No other company comes close to the list of features Sony offers here, and that's on top of excellent sound, improved fit and effective ANC.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DGVWF79V&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Sony+LinkBud+Fit+earbuds+for+%24128+%28%2472+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1NvbnktQ2FuY2VsaW5nLUhlYWRwaG9uZXMtRGV2ZWxvcGVkLVN1cHBvcnRlcnMvZHAvQjBER1ZXRjc5Vi8_&amp;signature=AQAAAUct0fMymGzuCi_VAPdvvQH83ZmX0Lw1X4ly04tQi2Ez&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Canceling-Headphones-Developed-Supporters%2Fdp%2FB0DGVWF79V%2F"><strong>Sony LinkBud Fit earbuds for $128 ($72 off):</strong></a> Sony's much smaller earbuds offer big sound and a lot of features for less than the 1000X model. These are a big improvement over the company's LinkBuds S, which were already a low-key hit for affordable earbuds.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DWHPBK42&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Sony+WF-CH710N+earbuds+for+%2478+%28%2442+off%29%3A&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARkuEukRj5NPiPwXZxNPCPDeN7tjut9-d6p7uRWIi3EE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-WF-C710N-Wireless-Noise-Canceling-Lightweight%2Fdp%2FB0DWHPBK42%2F"><strong>Sony WF-CH710N earbuds for $78 ($42 off):</strong></a> The CH710N is still quite new, but the earbuds are a steal at $80 for Prime Day. The compact, comfy design is a highlight, as are all the features Sony managed to pack in. Plus, they're available in a lovely transparent blue that allows you to see all of the internal components.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-sonos-prime-day-deals">Sonos Prime Day deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-bose-deals-also-available-at-bosecom">Prime Day Bose deals (also available at Bose.com)</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D8BZDPXB&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e682394