an the rest, putting this set just under $200. Plus, this model works with the company's soundbars for an enhanced living room listening experience.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-beats-prime-day-deals">Beats Prime Day deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CZPLV566&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Beats+Solo+4+headphones+for+%2498+%2850+percent+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ1pQTFY1NjY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmU3MWJjYjUtZTIwMC00MWMyLWEzMTUtZTY4MjM5NDRlMjc2Iiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ1pQTFY1NjYiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAe3kUsTOSt1eIPfmmoVirJd_lvdv92Mtpt5gCp-BVrc2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CZPLV566"><strong>Beats Solo 4 headphones for $98 (50 percent off):</strong></a> Beats' popular on-ear headphones are half off for Prime Day, which makes them a great deal for fans of that wear style. While they may look similar to their predecessor, the Solo 4 have improved sound and longer battery life compared to that older model.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DT2344N3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Beats+Powerbeats+Pro+2+earbuds+for+%24180+%2828+percent+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwRFQyMzQ0TjM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmU3MWJjYjUtZTIwMC00MWMyLWEzMTUtZTY4MjM5NDRlMjc2Iiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwRFQyMzQ0TjMiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAWhAGUU5rIIL3Lqo2s7ZKt_AOzaeCgt4Lgry8kDMUcR6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0DT2344N3"><strong>Beats Powerbeats Pro 2 earbuds for $180 (28 percent off):</strong></a> Apple's first earbuds with heart rate tracking are slightly discounted for Prime Day. This your chance to try the tech without paying full price. What's more, the Powerbeats Pro 2 have an improved design, the smarts of Apple's H2 chip and powerful bass.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-samsung-deals">Prime Day Samsung deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CF7GYNW2&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Samsung+Galaxy+Buds+FE+for+%2452+%2848+percent+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ0Y3R1lOVzI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmU3MWJjYjUtZTIwMC00MWMyLWEzMTUtZTY4MjM5NDRlMjc2Iiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ0Y3R1lOVzIiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAWZPugTtxCVeaAhPE4nvJQfKXSHeVp-d3yFVyvQT3X0L&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CF7GYNW2"><strong>Samsung Galaxy Buds FE for $52 (48 percent off):</strong></a> Samsung's budget earbuds are solid option if you're looking to spend less than $60. Like the Galaxy Buds 3 Pro, these are best-suited for Samsung devices where you'll find features like live translation and automatic switching.</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-apple-and-google-prime-day-deals">Apple and Google Prime Day deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DGHMNQ5Z&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Apple+AirPods+4+for+%2489+%2831+percent+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0FwcGxlLUhlYWRwaG9uZXMtQ2FuY2VsbGF0aW9uLVRyYW5zcGFyZW5jeS1QZXJzb25hbGl6ZWQvZHAvQjBER0hNTlE1Wi8_&amp;signature=AQAAAbrngH_qOQqsBTOJCaLZHBpoLlD0O8_eRmeCeRvs5eJx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Headphones-Cancellation-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0DGHMNQ5Z%2F"><strong>Apple AirPods 4 for $89 (31 percent off):</strong></a> The redesigned "regular" AirPods that debuted last year are currently available well below their normal $129 price tag. Here, you'll get the new, more comfortable shape as well as updated features.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DGJ7HYG1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Apple+AirPods+4+with+ANC+for+%24119+%2834+percent+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0FwcGxlLUhlYWRwaG9uZXMtQ2FuY2VsbGF0aW9uLVRyYW5zcGFyZW5jeS1QZXJzb25hbGl6ZWQvZHAvQjBER0o3SFlHMS8_&amp;signature=AQAAAT7RHvmXrE08LGjCOKVqexuIVL3ZcyjNIW3TCjOpyxtA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Headphones-Cancellation-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0DGJ7HYG1%2F"><strong>Apple AirPods 4 with ANC for $119 (34 percent off):</strong></a> And if you need some ANC to go with your AirPods, but don't want to go for the Pro 2, here's your best bet. These retain the open-style fit of regular AirPods but add surprisingly effective ANC to the mix.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DGJKT2X9&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Apple+AirPods+Max+%28USB-C%29+for+%24430+%2822+percent+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0FwcGxlLUhlYWRwaG9uZXMtQ2FuY2VsbGF0aW9uLVRyYW5zcGFyZW5jeS1QZXJzb25hbGl6ZWQvZHAvQjBER0pLVDJYOS8_&amp;signature=AQAAAQKELDSztrBpseh-xQOIJFE-vRi4TsyliTblZIHebWAc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Headphones-Cancellation-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0DGJKT2X9%2F"><strong>Apple AirPods Max (USB-C) for $430 (22 percent off):</strong></a> Apple's over-ear headphones are $119 off during Prime Day, which softens the blow to your wallet for this pricey set. They're comfy and offer a lot of handy features for Apple devices. Plus, you can unlock lossless listening with a wired connection.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D79ND3N7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Google+Pixel+Buds+Pro+2+for+%24160+%2830+percent+off%29%3A&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwRDc5TkQzTjc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmU3MWJjYjUtZTIwMC00MWMyLWEzMTUtZTY4MjM5NDRlMjc2Iiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwRDc5TkQzTjciLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAevMIaVU6V3_4c9PJoZtLOhovjstvVAE-XM_vnasHFrc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0D79ND3N7"><strong>Google Pixel Buds Pro 2 for $160 (30 percent off):</strong></a> The best earbuds for Pixel phone users are down to $160, which makes them a great purchase right now. Live translate and hands-free access to Gemini might be the highlight, but these earbuds have great sound and capable ANC too.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-prime-day-deals-on-dyson">Prime Day deals on Dyson</h2> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D7WZV5LV&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Dyson+OnTrac+headphones+for+%24300+%2840+percent+off%29%3A&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAc3UjYfd0H1dyHTlsgNJx4cPf65WH3sl7pGoe8Yn8iGs&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDyson-OnTracTM-Over-Wireless-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB0D7WZV5LV%2F"><strong>Dyson OnTrac headphones for $300 (40 percent off):</strong></a> This set isn't without its flaws, but I can understand why you'd be drawn to the almost infinitely customizable design and long battery life. There's also real-time hearing health features and the sound is crisp and clear even though it lacks depth and immersion.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-jbl-prime-day-deals">JBL Prime Day deals</h2> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0C4JBTM5B&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=JBL+Tour+One+M2+headphones+for+%24150+%2850+percent+off%29%3A&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcMxWjxaTX7kuTch-zCFQAVI3GRHvxudp6vr5fwZHdYB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FJBL-Tour-One-Cancelling-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB0C4JBTM5B"><strong>JBL Tour One M2 headphones for $150 (50 percent off):</strong></a> The biggest discount on JBL headphones or earbuds comes on the flagship over-hear Tour One M2. These ANC headphones have Smart Ambient sound, Smart Talk automatic pausing and other advanced features.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D3629RB6&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2e71bcb5-e200-41c2-a315-e6823944e276&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=JBL+Live+Beam+3+for+%24150+%2825+percent+off%29%3A&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAb9yF317_-9YtTX8R3UzK9rRW2SvihI3YlJurb7R0HET&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FJBL-Live-Beam-Noise-Cancelling-Closed-Stick%2Fdp%2FB0D3629RB6"><strong>JBL Live Beam 3 for $150 (25 percent off):</strong></a> If you're looking for a discounted way to get your hands on JBL's touchscreen earbud case, the Live Beam 3 is your chance. In addition to the fancy case, you'll get up to 12 hours of use on a charge, adaptive ANC and high-res audio compatibility.&nbsp;</p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/deals/prime-day-2025-the-best-headphone-and-earbud-deals-from-sony-beats-bose-and-more-for-the-last-day-of-the-sale-082347142.html?src=rss	2025-07-11 23:30:35	Billy Steele	f	2025-07-14 05:01:46.486316
378	14	The best Prime Day gaming deals on video games, hardware and more to get before the sale ends	https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-best-prime-day-gaming-deals-on-video-games-hardware-and-more-to-get-before-the-sale-ends-144228893.html?src=rss	<p>2025 has brought us the biggest <a href="https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-the-last-day-our-top-picks-on-headphones-tvs-robot-vacuums-and-more-120028336.html">Amazon Prime Day</a> ever and while today is your last chance to partake in the savings, there are still a ton of gaming deals to be had. We're talking about discounts on some of AMD's best gaming CPUs, award-winning titles like <em>Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom</em> and <em>Elden Ring</em> and brand new flagship systems from Alienware, Razer and more. So if you want to get a good price on everything from laptops to displays and all sorts of accessories, keep reading to see our handpicked list of the best gaming deals during Prime Day before they're gone forever (or at least until next year).</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-best-prime-day-deals-on-video-games">Best Prime Day deals on video games</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D8SDKKVW&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=29335a3d-e30a-462a-bc98-ed037a505006&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=The+Legend+of+Zelda%3A+Echoes+of+Wisdom+%28Nintendo+Switch%29+for+%2452+%28%248+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbpTmpSgHuRbyF2HS0MFzw2nXaj1Jx_gbJ6q1xH2y-eT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLegend-Zelda-Echoes-Wisdom-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB0D8SDKKVW%2F">The Legend of Zelda: Echoes of Wisdom (Nintendo Switch) for $52 ($8 off)</a></p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p>We rarely see discounts on first-party Nintendo games, especially when it comes to major franchises like The Legend of Zelda. But for Prime Day, <em>Echoes of Wisdom </em>is available for 15 percent off, which is even more impressive when you consider the game the game is less than a year old. Not only is this the first Zelda game to put our beloved princess in the spotlight (instead of Link), it offers a fun twist on the series' classic top-down action RPG formula thanks to Zelda's new ability to summon objects and monsters with the Tri-rod.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B097B2YWFX&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=29335a3d-e30a-462a-bc98-ed037a505006&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=The+Legend+of+Zelda%3A+Tears+of+the+Kingdom+%28Nintendo+Switch%29+for+%2459+%28%2411+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0xlZ2VuZC1aZWxkYS1CcmVhdGgtV2lsZC1OaW50ZW5kby1Td2l0Y2gvZHAvQjA5N0IyWVdGWC8_&amp;signature=AQAAAZObKvDFtvknCgsmHrreZiSPMWM0PsY_Y62kJ1iA-67F&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLegend-Zelda-Breath-Wild-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB097B2YWFX%2F">The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom (Nintendo Switch) for $59 ($11 off)</a></p> \n<p>Alternatively, if you are looking for something a bit faster paced, <em>The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom</em> may be one of the best sequels in recent video game history. And now for Prime Day, it's available for $11 off its normal retail price. Not only is this a great pickup for anyone who hasn't played it yet, it's also a great showcase of the Switch 2's capabilities as users can purchase a $10 upgrade pack (or get it for free if you have a subscription to Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack) that adds support for HDR, faster loading times, enhanced textures and smoother framerates.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D187PJHJ&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=29335a3d-e30a-462a-bc98-ed037a505006&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Star+Wars+Outlaws+-+Limited+Edition+%28Amazon+Exclusive%29%2C+PlayStation+5+for+%2429+%28%2431+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1N0YXItV2Fycy1PdXRsYXdzLUxpbWl0ZWQtRXhjbHVzaXZlLVBsYXlTdGF0aW9uL2RwL0IwRDE4N1BKSEo_&amp;signature=AQAAAX-qN5gYBtOyyhPWRRtLscr4ejDlCaDuK56BEb5KPI8N&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FStar-Wars-Outlaws-Limited-Exclusive-PlayStation%2Fdp%2FB0D187PJHJ">Star Wars Outlaws - Limited Edition (Amazon Exclusive), PlayStation 5 for $29 ($31 off)</a></p> \n<p>At full price, this game was easy to skip. But now that it's available for just $29 (half off its normal retail price), <em>Star Wars Outlaws</em> suddenly becomes a lot more interesting for fans of the franchise. You get to live out your dreams of being an intergalactic scoundrel while taking down bounties or battling secret crime syndicates. And because this is the limited edition, the game includes some pre-order rewards like the Kessel Run bonus pack and the Rogue Infiltrator bundle.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D47WTKPM&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=29335a3d-e30a-462a-bc98-ed037a505006&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Assassin%E2%80%99s+Creed+Shadows+-+Limited+Edition+for+PS5%2FXbox+Series+X+for+%2448+%28%2422+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0Fzc2Fzc2lucy1DcmVlZC1TaGFkb3dzLUxpbWl0ZWQtRXhjbHVzaXZlLVBsYXlTdGF0aW9uL2RwL0IwRDQ3V1RLUE0_&amp;signature=AQAAATCkYwhjfRZiCq1rRDO708tuJVNpcc8UHUJJ9MP-Nhiq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAssassins-Creed-Shadows-Limited-Exclusive-PlayStation%2Fdp%2FB0D47WTKPM">Assassin’s Creed Shadows - Limited Edition for PS5/Xbox Series X for $48 ($22 off)</a></p> \n<p>If you missed the latest entry in Ubisoft's most well-known franchise, this might be the time to jump in because for Prime Day, <em>Assassin's Creed Shadows</em> is available for $48, more than $20 off its regular retail price. This instalment has you explore feudal Japan as either the shinobi Naoe or the legendary samurai Yasuke while encountering some notable figures from the time period. If all you want is a wonderful world to sneak around in, it's hard to go wrong with Assassin's Creed on a discount.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CVSJ1JVC&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=29335a3d-e30a-462a-bc98-ed037a505006&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Elden+Ring%3A+Shadow+of+The+Erdtree+Edition+for+PS5%2FXbox+Series+X+for+%2460+%28%2420+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ1ZTSjFKVkM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjkzMzVhM2QtZTMwYS00NjJhLWJjOTgtZWQwMzdhNTA1MDA2Iiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ1ZTSjFKVkMiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAaxd5oPW2NpMiiiNxMrk39ikXMiK7Co2lEBPc-AZjyaO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CVSJ1JVC">Elden Ring: Shadow of The Erdtree Edition for PS5/Xbox Series X for $60 ($20 off)</a></p> \n<p><em>Elden Ring</em> is one of the most highly regarded games of this decade so far (and arguably of all time). For Prime Day, you can become a foul tarnished by picking up a version that includes the base game and the <em>Shadow of the Erdtree</em> expansion for $60. <em>Elden Ring</em> typically costs around $50 (though it's <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B07SMBNTSJ&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=29335a3d-e30a-462a-bc98-ed037a505006&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=down+to+%2430&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwN1NNQk5UU0o_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjkzMzVhM2QtZTMwYS00NjJhLWJjOTgtZWQwMzdhNTA1MDA2Iiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwN1NNQk5UU0oiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVXe7RYuLJI9-19qvptWHAg7IC7JNbO879yAuOARXWLm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07SMBNTSJ">down to $30</a> on PS4, PS5 and Xbox Series X for Prime Day) and the DLC will usually run you another $40, so that's a decent discount compared with buying them separately — or even the <em>Shadow of the Erdtree Edition </em>at its regular price.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DCKFWW1V&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=29335a3d-e30a-462a-bc98-ed037a505006&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Final+Fantasy+I-VI+Collection+Anniversary+Edition+for+PlayStation+and+Switch+for+%2445+%28%2430+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATlCZOrubfJH0fKzq3VUHJyEsob6HB9cPX9R6mKGZdnb&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFINAL-FANTASY-Collection-Anniversary-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB0DCKFWW1V">Final Fantasy I-VI Collection Anniversary Edition for PlayStation and Switch for $45 ($30 off)</a></p> \n<p>This collection of pixel remasters of the first six Final Fantasy games is discounted by $30 during Prime Day. 