Apple Pencil Pro and starts at 128GB of storage.</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p>\n </p> \n<p>We called it "reliable" and everything we "want in a small tablet" <a href="https://www.engadget.com/mobile/tablets/ipad-mini-7-review-safe-boring-and-everything-i-want-in-a-small-tablet-130039378.html">in our official review</a>. The speakers sound great, which has become standard with modern Apple devices, and the form factor makes it easy to hold for long periods of time without causing hand cramps. It's an iPad, just smaller.</p> \n<p>There are a couple of little caveats. The display is limited to a 60Hz refresh rate, which could impact some action-heavy games. There's also no Face ID here, which forces users to enter a password or use a fingerprint.&nbsp;</p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/deals/apples-latest-ipad-mini-is-down-to-a-record-low-price-for-prime-day-and-still-in-stock-100024613.html?src=rss	2025-07-11 13:36:26	Lawrence Bonk	f	2025-07-14 05:01:46.50219
392	14	The best Amazon Prime Day camera deals you can still get during the last day of the sale	https://www.engadget.com/cameras/the-best-amazon-prime-day-camera-deals-you-can-still-get-during-the-last-day-of-the-sale-104502374.html?src=rss	<p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-the-last-day-our-top-picks-on-headphones-tvs-robot-vacuums-and-more-120028336.html">Amazon Prime Day</a> is always a key period for camera buyers as any discount on such a major purchase is always helpful. Despite the tariffs, this year's sale is particularly strong for photography buffs, with big discounts on most of the major brands including some that don't normally offer deals.</p> \n<p>Some key deals include discounts on DJI drones, along with sales on models from Sony, Canon, GoPro and Nikon. Many of those cameras are ranked highly in our most recent <a href="https://www.engadget.com/cameras/best-cameras-151524327.html">camera guide</a>, like <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;linkText=Nikon%27s+Z6+III&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaK-ID-mZm9Do7gw4EAv1WFazWxnmGWbeXV4SdTFaHgE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1834803-REG%2Fnikon_z6_iii_mirrorless_camera.html">Nikon's Z6 III</a>, <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;linkText=Canon+EOS+R5+Mark+III&amp;_In0&amp;signature=AQAAAY96H_wIcbeS-fkOm1ZhIdK9MH0D2O0pofSIeJ9ktE8U&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1840289-REG%2Fcanon_6536c002_eos_r5_mark_ii.html%2F%3F">Canon EOS R5 Mark III</a> and the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0eee6f60-6f21-4ba6-b70e-cc15b39bf860&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Adorama&amp;linkText=GoPro+Hero+13+Black&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hZG9yYW1hLmNvbS9ncGhlcm8xMy5odG1sIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJiZTljZTY4Zi1iODVjLTRkOWItOWMyNS01ZjUxZjQ2MzA0OWQiLCJvcmlnaW5hbFVybCI6Imh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LmFkb3JhbWEuY29tL2dwaGVybzEzLmh0bWwifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAfUg3cBEAJ2y6KwBmwwyJ-rfRQAPO9Trq1OLFLfscB-V&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adorama.com%2Fgphero13.html">GoPro Hero 13 Black</a> — so feel free to check that out as you add items to your cart. Without further delay, here are the best Prime Day camera deals you can get for the last day of the sale.</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<h2 id="jump-link-best-prime-day-camera-deals">Best Prime Day camera deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0C5PGRP7V&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Canon+EOS+R100+with+RT-S18-45mm+lens+for+%24549+%2815+percent+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0Nhbm9uLVJGLVMxOC00NW1tLU1pcnJvcmxlc3MtQ29udGludW91cy1MaWdodHdlaWdodC9kcC9CMEM1UEdSUDdWL3JlZj1zcl8xXzM_&amp;signature=AQAAAQsanFmKVwpQtduBd9jg-vfFixsvFab-7Cg4Hla_ngt3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCanon-RF-S18-45mm-Mirrorless-Continuous-Lightweight%2Fdp%2FB0C5PGRP7V%2Fref%3Dsr_1_3">Canon EOS R100 with RT-S18-45mm lens for $549 (15 percent off)</a>: Canon's EOS R100 is the only modern mirrorless camera you can get with a kit lens for under $600. It comes with a 24-megapixel APS-C sensor that delivers great picture quality with Canon's pleasing skin tones.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BTTV6CT1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Canon+EOS+R50+with+RF-S18-45mm+lens+for+%24749+%2815+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeV0-Hd0zM6tIY1uvTMgTgvMLJQfqhQ5hAj-dtF4oHeZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCanon-Mirrorless-RF-S18-45mm-Smartphone-Connection%2Fdp%2FB0BTTV6CT1%2Fref%3Dsr_1_3">Canon EOS R50 with RF-S18-45mm lens for $749 (15 percent off)</a>: Canon's 24-megapixel APS-C EOS R50 is great for travel, parties, street photography and more thanks to the portable size and built-in flash. It offers nice image quality with warm, human friendly photos and is capable for creators as well with 4K 30fps supersampled video, with 10-bit and HDR capability.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BHM3DWKN&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=OM+System+OM-5+for+%24899+%2825+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfCinHqn8uZrV1z_5BrWMvSLD7T_YvWijwA_Iz0VWueM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOM-SYSTEM-Mirrorless-Camera-Black%2Fdp%2FB0BHM3DWKN">OM System OM-5 for $899 (25 percent off)</a>: For creators on a budget, the 20-megapixel, Micro Four Thirds OM-5 from OM System (formerly Olympic) is a great option at this price. It lets you shoot 4K video and 20MP stills at up to 10 fps. The design is nice with a full complement of manual controls, a fully articulating display and 7.5 stops of built-in stabilization.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D4FBF5NK&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Panasonic+Lumix+S9+for+%241%2C298+%2813+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAW8HfSq2tp2ovBigIj-B2rUBcYy2eNlGdAXp2vsyIRtb&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPanasonic-Mirrorless-Camera-24-2MP-Technology%2Fdp%2FB0D4FBF5NK%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1_sspa">Panasonic Lumix S9 for $1,298 (13 percent off)</a>: The S9 may be Panasonic's smallest full-frame camera but it comes with the same 24MP sensor and similar video features to the popular S5 II. To that end, it offers up to 6.2K video, in-body stabilization and reliable autofocus. The key feature though is a special LUT button that lets you easily choose a custom cinematic look designed by professional creators.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0BL7ZVY78&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Canon+EOS+R6+Mark+II+for+%241%2C899+%285+percent+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQkw3WlZZNzg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYmU5Y2U2OGYtYjg1Yy00ZDliLTljMjUtNWY1MWY0NjMwNDlkIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQkw3WlZZNzgiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQwcXIQRlpdJcEZe6utwXsYzihumV6cxOnlNA7-b3kBb&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BL7ZVY78">Canon EOS R6 Mark II for $1,899 (5 percent off)</a>: Canon's R6 Mark II offers a great mix of video and photography features. You can now shoot RAW stills at up to 40 fps and video specs are equally solid with sharp full-sensor 4K at up to 60 fps. It comes with in-body stabilization that's great for video and photos and autofocus is quicker and more versatile than ever.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D77SL8CY&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Nikon+Z6+III+for+%242%2C197+%2812+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQl78sBuE84i6sKYMq7twC5IyT6x7nFcuZUrz-uhaBo0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNikon-Full-Frame-mirrorless-Internal-Recording%2Fdp%2FB0D77SL8CY%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1">Nikon Z6 III for $2,197 (12 percent off)</a>: Nikon's Z6 III is the best hybrid mirrorless camera for the money, thanks to the incredible performance of the 24-megapixel partially stacked sensor. You can shoot RAW bursts at up to 20 fps in electronic shutter mode while nailing sharp shots thanks to the much-improved autofocus. On the video side, it supports 6K RAW at up to 60 fps, or 4K 120p. All of that makes it ideal for creators and photographers alike, with the only drawback being the reduced resolution.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B09JZT6YK5&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Sony+A7+IV+for+%242%2C198+%2819+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUia2SB7qGLSewTikTf7A_Krrh_x167v-IcnBdkAhg1Z&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Full-frame-Mirrorless-Interchangeable-Camera%2Fdp%2FB09JZT6YK5%2Fref%3Dsr_1_3">Sony A7 IV for $2,198 (19 percent off)</a>: It beats many rivals with 33 megapixels of resolution rather than 24, with image quality much improved overall. Video is now up to par with rivals with 4K at up to 60p with 10 bit 4:2:2 quality. Autofocus is incredible for both video and stills, and the in-body stabilization does a good job. The biggest drawback is rolling shutter that limits the use of the electronic shutter.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DL6KN2PH&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Canon+EOS+R5+Mark+II+for+%243%2C999+%28%24300+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYRGQomzcVaZy_DXNUWQNP1-JP3dBrYEhnZBAoOGuRA-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCanon-Mirrorless-Camera-Lithium-Ion-Battery%2Fdp%2FB0DL6KN2PH%2Fref%3Dsr_1_4">Canon EOS R5 Mark II for $3,999 ($300 off)</a>: It's company’s best camera in years thanks to improvements in areas like autofocus and video. It comes with a high-resolution 45-megapixel stacked sensor, but still lets you shoot blackout-free bursts at up to 30 fps — and most of the shots will be sharp thanks to the updated autofocus with AI tracking. Video is also strong with up to 8K 60p RAW and 4K 120 fps shooting.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-best-prime-day-action-cam-and-drone-deals">Best Prime Day action cam and drone deals</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B07FTG84SW&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=DJI+Osmo+Mobile+7P+gimbal+for+%24125+%2815+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVibdUdMbodXMhUKxcC9DsPcmnupIMGh4ta5teXCD42k&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDJI-6941565997517-Osmo-Mobile-Gimbal%2Fdp%2FB07FTG84SW">DJI Osmo Mobile 7P gimbal for $125 (15 percent off)</a><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0B7XCG225&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=%3A&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARqoSuRFpFD5xJ6FvOVIF5FA569SHv-eHL3RvXDic2Nv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSmartphone-Stabilizer-Magnetic-Portable-Foldable%2Fdp%2FB0B7XCG225">: </a>This three-axis gimbal keeps your smartphone video as smooth as can be with DJI's ActiveTrack 7.0, and includes a magnetic snapping mechanism so you can install your mobile device in seconds. The latest feature is native tracking that follows you around, thanks to the included Multifunctional Module.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0C783YNW7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=DJI+Osmo+Action+4+for+%24209+%2830+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAa5SEekgkENDECLm2TKqQjjLkxkx29GiSqY-sucz7uGY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDJI-Waterproof-Low-Light-Performance-Long-Lasting%2Fdp%2FB0C783YNW7%2Fref%3Dsr_1_3">DJI Osmo Action 4 for $209 (30 percent off)</a>: DJI's Osmo Action 4 is a tremendous deal at this price, as you're not giving up much in comparison to the most recent model, the Action 5. It has the same big 1/1.3-inch sensor that delivers excellent video quality, especially in low light. It also features a D-LogM profile to boost dynamic range, DJI's excellent clip-on mount and high-quality 4K 120p video.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DCM34GXX&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=GoPro+Hero+13+Black+for+%24329+%2823+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAe2t13mwkvS7qXx89GE0pPBIbF7BWeT7wRMnKH0dRIkR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoPro-HERO13-Black-Compatability-HB%2Fdp%2FB0DCM34GXX%2Fref%3Dsr_1_3">GoPro Hero 13 Black for $329 (23 percent off)</a>: GoPro’s Hero 13 Black is now available with a new family of modular lenses called the HB series (ultra-wide, anamorphic and macro), making it far more versatile for action creators. It also has a slightly bigger battery that allows longer capture times, up to 90 minutes for 4K 30fps video. Other specs remain the same, including up to 5.3K at 60fps in 10-bit color, along with the excellent Hypersmooth stabilization.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DBQBMQH2&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Insta360+X4+for+%24349+%2830+percent%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0luc3RhMzYwLVN0YW5kYXJkLUJ1bmRsZS1XYXRlcnByb29mLVN0YWJpbGl6YXRpb24vZHAvQjBEQlFCTVFIMi9yZWY9c3JfMV8xX3NzcGE_&amp;signature=AQAAAe_EweQehqZ0kLZsrD0JUan7B6IdZZVRE62J6OtU0MBp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FInsta360-Standard-Bundle-Waterproof-Stabilization%2Fdp%2FB0DBQBMQH2%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1_sspa">Insta360 X4 for $349 (30 percent)</a>: Insta360 simply dominates the 360-degree category, thanks to its ability to capture action at up to 8K 30fps or 5.7K at 60fps — providing <a href="https://www.engadget.com/insta360-x4-release-date-price-first-impressions-130001066.html">more detail</a> when you reframe it to 16:9. At the same time, the Me Mode that produces flat video (with automatic selfie stick removal) has been upgraded from a maximum 2.7K 30fps to 4K 30fps. It also offers solid battery life, waterproofing to 10m and a free editing app.&nbsp;</p> \n<h2 id="jump-link-best-prime-day-deals-on-camera-accessories">Best Prime Day deals on camera accessories</h2> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0D2QDXR3W&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=K%26F+Concept+25L+backpack+for+%2450+%2817+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASGDuVFIqEC-zA9eOrS3cMTcr_8TCQzIAyefy7iUxAe1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FConcept-Photographers-Raincover-Compartment-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB0D2QDXR3W">K&amp;F Concept 25L backpack for $50 (17 percent off)</a>: A large 25L three-tiered camera bag that can hold multiple cameras, lenses and drones. It has quick side access and features durable materials with a rain cover, making it great for outdoor travel, weddings or vlogging.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CCSY4235&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Lexar+256GB+Professional+Silver+Pro+V60+memory+card+for+%2451+%2832+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaVVcwrTt_bNTl128pCeZaDq_jYwQHI9T5vcaDM8lMZC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLexar-Professional-Photographer-Videographer-LSDSIPR256G-BNNNU%2Fdp%2FB0CCSY4235%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1_sspa">Lexar 256GB Professional Silver Pro V60 memory card for $51 (32 percent off)</a>: An excellent compromise between speed and value with up to 280MB/s read and 160MB/s write speeds.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0B63VTW46&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=SmallRig+71-inch+Camera+Tripod+with+360+ball+head+for+%2456+%2820+percent+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL1NtYWxsUmlnLUZvbGRhYmxlLURldGFjaGFibGUtQWRqdXN0YWJsZS1QaG9uZS0zOTM1L2RwL0IwQjYzVlRXNDY_&amp;signature=AQAAAS5hUXAnhCBADcViToqqdmtQoTaEZmJkMeO1usclqRXT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSmallRig-Foldable-Detachable-Adjustable-Phone-3935%2Fdp%2FB0B63VTW46">SmallRig 71-inch Camera Tripod with 360 ball head for $56 (20 percent off)</a>: Two-in-one tripod monopod with a head that adjusts 360 degrees so you can take photos at any angle horizontally or vertically.&nbsp;</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B07L755X9G&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Elgato+Key+Light+2800+lumens+for+%24133+%2826+percent+off%29&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0VsZ2F0by1LZXktTGlnaHQtUHJvZmVzc2lvbmFsLWFwcC1hZGp1c3RhYmxlL2RwL0IwN0w3NTVYOUc_&amp;signature=AQAAAdbkXN1B5F4Ye6EDvEYNiwg0ln4yDG-S0CS6b5PlVB9P&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElgato-Key-Light-Professional-app-adjustable%2Fdp%2FB07L755X9G">Elgato Key Light 2800 lumens for $133 (26 percent off)</a>: For presentations or simple studio shoots, you get a silent, low-heat studio light with high output and a 2900-7000K temperature range. It's controllable by WiFi and has an opal glass face for glare-free diffusion.&nbsp;</p> \n<h3 id="jump-link-expired-deals">Expired deals</h3> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B07FTPX71F&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=DJI+Neo+drone+for+%24159+%2820+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY_WBK2p8D39a5-bsmDhCXyIiBvMiM29tfmZHiZ1ISDf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDJI-QuickShots-Stabilized-Propeller-Controller-Free%2Fdp%2FB07FTPX71F">DJI Neo drone for $159 (20 percent off)</a>: The DJI Neo may be an inexpensive, beginner-friendly drone, but has powerful features like subject tracking and quick shots. It can shoot video at up to 4K 30 fps and is quick and maneuverable, though it's also fairly loud. You can also grab one with <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DDS1368S&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=three+batteries+and+a+charger+for+%24229+%2821+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbi3Iv4zxq5hq-9L-jUb9o8qCnLGm_fBee-xWMgYE4XR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDJI-QuickShots-Stabilized-Propeller-Controller-Free%2Fdp%2FB0DDS1368S">three batteries and a charger for $229 (21 percent off)</a>.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0F4WZ3Q2J&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=DJI+Mini+4K+drone+for+%24309+%2821+percent+off%29%3A&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcYRqCvzdP5kR00RUiO2f1G4NTUXrddLfUHfg_wwdv_H&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDJI-Stabilization-Transmission-Batteries-QuickShots%2Fdp%2FB0F4WZ3Q2J%2F">DJI Mini 4K drone for $309 (21 percent off):</a> The Mini 4 weighs less than 249 grams so it doesn't require a permit, but can still shoot 4K video at up to 30 fps or 2.7K at 60 fps with three-axis stabilization. It can fly up to 31 minutes on a charge and has one-tap movements like dronie, helix and panoramic shooting.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CH3P9K1X&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=be9ce68f-b85c-4d9b-9c25-5f51f463049d&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Elgato+Prompter+for+%24190+%2837+percent+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVxG26HVY1K6H05ptJTsiCDL7dztK9FlpL-Bkg2hxZMt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElgato-Prompter-Teleprompter-Built-Smartphone%2Fdp%2FB0CH3P9K1X">Elgato Prompter for $190 (37 percent off)</a>: Whether you're a creator on YouTube or present on Zoom, the Elgato Prompter is an elegant and popular choice thanks to the built-in display that allows you to read scripts while looking at the camera. Support more cameras than ever, even with wide lenses and features an easy setup.</p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/cameras/the-best-amazon-prime-day-camera-deals-you-can-still-get-during-the-last-day-of-the-sale-104502374.html?src=rss	2025-07-11 13:16:26	Steve Dent	f	2025-07-14 05:01:46.503249
393	14	The Bose QuietComfort headphones are still on sale for $199 on the last day of Prime Day	https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-bose-quietcomfort-headphones-are-still-on-sale-for-199-on-the-last-day-of-prime-day-103010111.html?src=rss	<p>Noise-cancelling headphones are a must if you're traveling or hoping to get some work done without distractions wherever you may be. <a href="https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-the-last-day-our-top-picks-on-headphones-tvs-robot-vacuums-and-more-120028336.html">Prime Day deals</a> include a bunch of the most popular headphones and earbuds for less, like the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CCZC9J1V&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=2445ae7f-7634-40ef-9468-439a56ecaa01&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Bose+QuietComfort+headphones&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ0NaQzlKMVY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjQ0NWFlN2YtNzYzNC00MGVmLTk0NjgtNDM5YTU2ZWNhYTAxIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ0NaQzlKMVYiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAReePg77n211-SdpcyMl2eABUTJatzBImEaEd0OnoWvg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CCZC9J1V">Bose QuietComfort headphones</a>. These cans are down to $199 right now, or 42 percent off their usual price, and they're still in stock during the last day of the sale.</p> \n<p>These QuietComfort headphones include active noise cancellation (ANC) and multipoint connectivity for switching between various audio sources. There's a fully customizable EQ that can be adjusted via the affiliated app. The battery life is fantastic here, offering 24 hours of use per charge. Also, there's a quick-charge feature that provides 2.5 hours of use from a 15 minute trip to the outlet.</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p>\n </p> \n<p>As to the name, these cans include plush, padded earcups and an adjustable padded band. They should be comfortable for all-day use. We haven't gotten a chance to review this particular model, but we loved the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-headphones-review-a-new-spin-on-a-reliable-formula-160009025.html">QuietComfort Ultra headphones</a>. They even found a spot on our list of the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/audio/headphones/best-headphones-wireless-bluetooth-120543205.html">best wireless headphones</a>. Bose typically <a href="https://www.engadget.com/audio/headphones/bose-quietcomfort-earbuds-2024-review-a-more-affordable-anc-ace-150018195.html">makes great stuff</a>.</p> \n<p>The headphones do come with a microphone, but some reviews suggest the quality is a bit off when compared to rival units. However, it still gets the job done for a quick phone call or whatever. The major downside here is the price, as $350 is a whole lot of cheddar. Luckily, today's deal calms some of that sticker shock.</p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-bose-quietcomfort-headphones-are-still-on-sale-for-199-on-the-last-day-of-prime-day-103010111.html?src=rss	2025-07-11 13:11:27	Lawrence Bonk	f	2025-07-14 05:01:46.504869
394	14	The Apple iPad Air M3 is still in stock and $120 off for Prime Day	https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-apple-ipad-air-m3-is-still-in-stock-and-120-off-for-prime-day-094516584.html?src=rss	<p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/">Prime Day</a> is almost over and that means you can still save a ton on some of the latest gadgets on the market through the end of the day today. Case in point: the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DZ74YQ1V&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=0fd96e92-00a5-4838-8f18-2ca96980d3f2&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Apple+iPad+Air+with+M3+chip&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwRFo3NFlRMVY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMGZkOTZlOTItMDBhNS00ODM4LThmMTgtMmNhOTY5ODBkM2YyIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwRFo3NFlRMVYiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATbwj0P_IWqKEC636uTW_DYfSC1qK-yGR2Ha06ZorqVq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0DZ74YQ1V">Apple iPad Air with M3 chip</a>. The slab that was released this March is down to $479 right now, which is a 20 percent discount from its usual price.</p> \n<p>This model remains our overall pick for <a href="https://www.engadget.com/mobile/tablets/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">best iPad</a>, and we gave it a score of 89 out of 100 in <a href="https://www.engadget.com/mobile/tablets/ipad-air-m3-review-a-modest-update-thats-still-easy-to-recommend-130045196.html">our review</a>. The powerful M3 chip was the star of the show. Testing shows the M3 is about 16 percent more powerful in both single- and multi-core performance than the M2.</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p>\n </p> \n<p>The iPad Air is still Apple's most affordable large-screen iPad, which makes multitasking easier than on the base iPad. The M3 iPad Air is also compatible with the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/mobile/tablets/apple-updates-the-ipad-air-with-an-m3-chip-and-a-new-magic-keyboard-140525345.html">new Magic Keyboard</a> for iPad Air, which is a much-improved design based on the keyboard that was introduced alongside the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/ipad-pro-2024-review-so-very-nice-and-so-very-expensive-210012937.html">iPad Pro M4</a>.</p> \n<p>This is the lowest we've ever seen the iPad Air with M3, so if you're in the market for an iPad, you'd be hard-pressed to find a better deal than this one. Most people will be happy with the iPad Air, but there are a couple of other Prime Day iPad deals worth considering too. The cheapest iPad, the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DZ75TN5F&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=0fd96e92-00a5-4838-8f18-2ca96980d3f2&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=iPad+A16&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwRFo3NVRONUYvcmVmPWZzX2FfaXB0Ml91czQ_&amp;signature=AQAAAX9gE5WYg1QWByx9AYB1rAD6jC9xFy2pJfclTJBT_SGn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0DZ75TN5F%2Fref%3Dfs_a_ipt2_us4">iPad A16</a>, is on sale for $280 right now, and the smallest iPad, the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DK3YF38G&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=0fd96e92-00a5-4838-8f18-2ca96980d3f2&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=iPad+mini&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF