401	14	Our favorite smart air purifier is still available for $37 off in this Prime Day deal	https://www.engadget.com/deals/our-favorite-smart-air-purifier-is-still-available-for-37-off-in-this-prime-day-deal-143224074.html?src=rss	<p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals-for-the-last-day-our-top-picks-on-headphones-tvs-robot-vacuums-and-more-120028336.html">Prime Day</a> is almost a wrap, but you can still save on a bunch of our favorite tech — and yes, much of it is still in stock even this late in the game. One of the best deals we're tracking is on the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B08R794ZMX&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=e70c4fc0-2755-4281-80f0-9d5d2c28deff&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Levoit+Core+400S+air+purifier&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0xFVk9JVC1QdXJpZmllci1BbGxlcmdpZXMtQ29yZS00MDBTL2RwL0IwOFI3OTRaTVg_&amp;signature=AQAAAU1TKyoi2Jj0S8GPb7nK24zkiriZlR2z4Yo9NpzjQXNV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLEVOIT-Purifier-Allergies-Core-400S%2Fdp%2FB08R794ZMX">Levoit Core 400S air purifier</a>. At $183, the device is $37 off. It's not quite the lowest price we've seen for this model. However, it's not too far off that mark of $176.</p> \n<p>The Levoit Core 400S is our current pick for the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/smart-home/best-air-purifier-120040002.html">best air purifier overall</a>. Sure, it might not have the prettiest design of all the options we have tested and the companion app might have a little too much going on. But the Core 400S does its job and does it well.</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p>\n </p> \n<p>This smart air purifier is slated to clean the atmosphere in spaces of up to 1,733 square feet in as little as one hour. The Core 400S has a cylindrical shape with vents at the top and a touch display that shows air quality readings. You'll be able to get a sense of the current air quality in your space at a glance with a color-changing ring that will light up in blue, green, orange or red. The 360-degree filtration system is said to be capable of capturing over 99.9 percent of pollutants as small as 0.3 microns, such as dust, pet dander and pollen.</p> \n<p>There is an auto mode that should suffice for maintaining air quality, but the Core 400S is compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant voice controls too. The fan isn't too loud, even when it's operating at maximum speed — the volume topped out at 62dB in our testing.</p> \n<p>Meanwhile, at $50 each, the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0B5YZ2ZKC&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=e70c4fc0-2755-4281-80f0-9d5d2c28deff&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=air+filter+replacements&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0NvcmUtUmVwbGFjZW1lbnQtTEVWT0lULUNvcmU0MDBTLVJGLUxSRi1DNDAxUy1XVVMvZHAvQjBCNVlaMlpLQy8_&amp;signature=AQAAAXUfGfNiOf8itbiQCk2ZXt1cj8hXk168UHLEsToL_EJ9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCore-Replacement-LEVOIT-Core400S-RF-LRF-C401S-WUS%2Fdp%2FB0B5YZ2ZKC%2F">air filter replacements</a> aren't too expensive compared with those from many of Levoit's competitors. You can also find other <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=e70c4fc0-2755-4281-80f0-9d5d2c28deff&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Levoit+Prime+Day+deals&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdkDVNZWiSSE7gIB6zcGIy6yfPIhv9IkOJ7c4-uNEJqH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fstores%2Fpage%2F36E5D100-D40D-4618-AEA6-A8FF8AD39805%2Fdeals">Levoit Prime Day deals</a> on Amazon right now that include more air purifiers, <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DQKQ3F2C&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=e70c4fc0-2755-4281-80f0-9d5d2c28deff&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=cordless+vacuums&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAf972jBWZ5nKN1hp75HJqyWFoaSJFL76SrdgToeje9pb&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLEVOIT-Cordless-Tangle-Resistant-Lightweight-Motorized%2Fdp%2FB0DQKQ3F2C">cordless vacuums</a> and more.</p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/deals/our-favorite-smart-air-purifier-is-still-available-for-37-off-in-this-prime-day-deal-143224074.html?src=rss	2025-07-11 12:16:26	Kris Holt	f	2025-07-14 05:01:46.511919
402	14	The Apple Watch Series 10 is still in stock and cheaper than ever for Prime Day	https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-apple-watch-series-10-is-still-in-stock-and-cheaper-than-ever-for-prime-day-152348381.html?src=rss	<p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/">Amazon Prime Day</a> is just about over, but there are plenty of deals to shop through the end of the sale tonight. Right now you can pick up the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DGJ5KQL7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=7a20905a-8a46-4000-b0e4-116c01c5067a&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Apple+Watch+Series+10&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATJ0qjT1twNK8yBUCvAaGogQprmPdDo6cM_Fih8BdXdX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0DGJ5KQL7%2F">Apple Watch Series 10</a> for $120 off its normal price. That’s the lowest we’ve ever seen it, and trust us, 30 percent off a current-generation Apple product is not easy to come by.</p> \n<p>It’s hard to believe that the Apple Watch is already ten years old. It seems like only yesterday that <a href="https://www.engadget.com/2014-09-09-iwatch-hands-on.html">we got our hands</a> on the first generation, and now the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/wearables/apple-watch-series-10-review-legacy-and-sequel-in-equal-measure-120021405.html">Apple Watch Series 10</a> is counting the days until the next generation is announced. Whether you’re looking to upgrade from an older Apple Watch or this is your first time buying an Apple smartwatch (though keep in mind an iPhone is required to use an Apple Watch), this sale is a great opportunity to pick one up at a fantastic value.</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p>\n </p> \n<p>The tenth generation of the Apple Watch represents a powerhouse of computing on your wrist. In our <a href="https://www.engadget.com/wearables/apple-watch-series-10-review-legacy-and-sequel-in-equal-measure-120021405.html">hands-on review</a>, we loved the comprehensive health and fitness tracking capabilities on the watch, which has been a strong niche for Apple. We were sad to see the blood oxygen app removed following a<a href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-will-remove-blood-oxygen-app-from-watch-series-9-and-ultra-2-to-evade-us-import-ban-194517839.html"> patent dispute</a>, but features like fall detection and sleep apnea tracking are still intact. It’s also the thinnest Apple Watch yet, feeling more like a slim accessory than a bulky gadget. We gave the Apple Watch 10 a score of 90 out of 100, and it remains our top pick for <a href="https://www.engadget.com/wearables/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">best smartwatch</a>.</p> \n<p>If you're looking to send less, consider the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DGHZJVYY&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=7a20905a-8a46-4000-b0e4-116c01c5067a&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Apple+Watch+SE&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYNeSyOuAVQoZgNfnQu5HKm7RFZBruyodXXfeil-XHdX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0DGHZJVYY%2Fref%3Dfs_a_wt2_us4">Apple Watch SE</a>. You can grab one for only $169 right now, or 32 percent off its usual price. It doesn't have all the bells, whistles and extra sensors that the Series 10 does, but you'll still get the core Apple Watch experience with excellent activity tracking, heart rate monitoring, smart alerts and more.</p> \n<p>\n </p> \n<p></p>This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/deals/the-apple-watch-series-10-is-still-in-stock-and-cheaper-than-ever-for-prime-day-152348381.html?src=rss	2025-07-11 12:11:26	Andre Revilla	f	2025-07-14 05:01:46.512898
403	14	Amazon Prime Day vacuum deals discount the Dyson V15 Detect Plus by $180	https://www.engadget.com/deals/amazon-prime-day-vacuum-deals-discount-the-dyson-v15-detect-plus-by-180-121534595.html?src=rss	<p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/">Amazon Prime Day</a> will be over soon, but heavy-hitting sales on pretty expensive tech are still around. There are great deals to be had on home appliances like the <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CT97D9R2&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=f6591e34-9024-4711-a9ec-2b14254afa73&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Dyson+V15+Detect+Plus&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ1Q5N0Q5UjI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjY1OTFlMzQtOTAyNC00NzExLWE5ZWMtMmIxNDI1NGFmYTczIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ1Q5N0Q5UjIiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbmsiLCJmZWF0dXJlSWQiOiJ0ZXh0LWxpbmsifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXR0y8suXRQVHTQTy1U-rCMl1OZ9gEp1GShfLBr9JmWW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CT97D9R2">Dyson V15 Detect Plus</a>. Dyson vacuums are not exactly known for being the most affordable, so now is a good time to consider buying one.</p> \n<p>Advanced designs and brand name recognition make these household gadgets a premium product. That's why we're always excited when the best ones receive great sales. The Dyson V15 Detect was <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/smart-home/best-cordless-vacuum-130007125.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly90cmVsbG8uY29tLw&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAIe8WCM9HR-Ijz209x2YuAOl4laBEkbLBEQ357lCUkXNV_C3ewwJCaW5vzRRJRjsPlZq3fX4t-BfvHN8csUARIR6QIBuB-MBWgG3nqi2EMSDPSYnF506_OfxMzMrbDp239mNSM63Xy0KdZaaQ9K83WimhVHU_UUiuByVDRlmTH-b">our best overall pick</a> for a cordless vacuum in 2025, and it's getting a huge markdown for Amazon Prime Day. Normally retailing for $750, this powerful cordless model is on sale to Prime members for just $570, which is only $20 more than its all-time-low price.</p> <span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>\n<p>\n </p> \n<p>We loved the <a href="https://www.engadget.com/dyson-v15-detect-230145131-230145683.html">Dyson V15 Detect</a> and it earned a slot in our <a href="https://www.engadget.com/home/smart-home/best-cordless-vacuum-130007125.html">best cordless vacuums</a> guide. The Plus model on sale during Prime Day is the same vacuum with more accessories. The suction power on the V15 Detect Plus is really impressive, especially for a cordless vacuum. For anyone with pets, good suction should be a strong consideration when selecting a vacuum, and we were thoroughly impressed with the pet hair this model picked up in our tests from both hardwood and carpet.</p> \n<p>The Fluffy Optic hard surface cleaning head comes with a laser that illuminates the ground in front of you as you vacuum. It does a frighteningly good job of highlighting just how much dust, hair and other debris have collected on your hardwood or tile floors that you might not have seen. For a shocking look at just how much stuff is on your floors, try vacuuming with the lights off.</p> \n<p>The V15 Detect Plus gets its namesake from a handy LCD display screen on the main body of the vacuum that tells you exactly how many particles across different size ranges the vacuum has detected since you started cleaning. In practice, this doesn't add anything to the functionality of the device, but it sheds a light on just how much stuff you've picked up.</p> \n<p>Other <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=f6591e34-9024-4711-a9ec-2b14254afa73&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName