7cotB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChipolo-POP-Tracker-Tag-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB0DZXTLD38%2F">$25 Chipolo Pop</a>, or a <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0DZXXB7KF&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=dcf76021-3f48-4860-8e53-5c09054d98d5&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=%2476+pack+of+four&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0NoaXBvbG8tUE9QLVRyYWNrZXItVGFnLUNvbXBhdGlibGUvZHAvQjBEWlhYQjdLRi8_&amp;signature=AQAAAZc4QRB0N8eH4hdlLcUepgMfgWSY4dGdzGluNXwh15LE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FChipolo-POP-Tracker-Tag-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB0DZXXB7KF%2F">$76 pack of four</a>, for anyone that wants a reliable Bluetooth tracker that works well with any ecosystem.</p></li> \n <li><p>A <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CCC69HN3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=dcf76021-3f48-4860-8e53-5c09054d98d5&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=%2416+Samsung+SmartTag+2&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQG0KDfZeczmSzoZIvroDvTusUeRw2lA_PAp2Kx7ktjY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-SmartTag2-Bluetooth-Tracker-Tracking%2Fdp%2FB0CCC69HN3%2F">$16 Samsung SmartTag 2</a>, or a <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B0CCBP3XN8&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=dcf76021-3f48-4860-8e53-5c09054d98d5&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=%2462+pack+of+four&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAd12wjxl4E_ESoXm1OJy0FqBNMlUO_E-oqv-gweq5vrO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-SmartTag2-Bluetooth-Tracker-Tracking%2Fdp%2FB0CCBP3XN8%2F">$62 pack of four</