e-Pencil-USB-C%2F5127015143">Walmart</a>.</p> \n<p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;itemId=amazon_B07K1WWBJK&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=5c2b9c33-9a87-45ff-b978-e41b8f7a90a2&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;linkText=Apple+Pencil+%282nd+gen%29+for+%2490+%28%2439+off%29&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUTFc3LgheqBJMwbIJxR86NgC70fvelSAhcQS0mhutwg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation%2Fdp%2FB07K1WWBJK"><strong>Apple Pencil (2nd gen) for $90 ($39 off)</strong></a>: The Second gen Pencil both attaches and charges magnetically, supports tilt and pressure sensitivity and allows for tool changes with a tap of the flat edge. It’s an older pencil and isn’t compatible with the latest iPad models. This is the lowest price we’ve tracked this year, but it went as low as $80 for last year’s Black Friday sales.</p> \n<p><strong>Read more Apple coverage</strong>:</p> \n<ul> \n <li><p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/audio/headphones/best-airpods-100041810.html">The best AirPods</a></p></li> \n <li><p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/wearables/best-apple-watch-160005462.html">The best Apple Watches</a></p></li> \n <li><p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/computing/laptops/best-macbook-140032524.html">The best MacBooks</a></p></li> \n <li><p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/mobile/smartphones/best-iphone-160012979.html">The best iPhones</a></p></li> \n <li><p><a href="https://www.engadget.com/mobile/tablets/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">The best iPads</a></p></li> \n</ul> \n<p><em>Follow </em><a href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a><em> on X for the latest </em><a href="https://www.engadget.com/deals/"><em>tech deals</em></a><em> and </em><a href="https://www.engadget.com/best-tech/"><em>buying advice</em></a><em>.</em></p>This article origina