3b-bfe1-4d56-bd6e-3885c642b140&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=9bc3966d-0466-4076-9841-6bc2e9920c17&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Verizon&amp;linkText=Verizon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASMthVwAD0V4D1fAhqM63fkwfPQqXLg2a5ejyVL0GPbi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verizon.com%2Fproducts%2Fnintendo-switch-2-light-blue-and-light-red%2F">Verizon</a> (service required)</p></li> \n</ul> \n<h2 id="jump-link-where-to-buy-nintendo-switch-2-games-and-accessories">Where to buy Nintendo Switch 2 games and accessories</h2> \n<p>Nintendo is selling a number of Switch 2 accessories alongside the console, from <a href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/nintendo/switch-2-pro-controller-review-nintendos-best-gamepad-simply-costs-too-much-151330215.html">its (pricey) Pro Controller</a> to cases to cameras for the new <a href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/nintendo/the-nintendo-switch-2-offers-built-in-voice-chat-and-screensharing-133334225.html">GameChat feature</a>. Most of these became available on June 5. The same goes for games like <em>Mario Kart World </em>and the Switch 2 version of <a href="https://www.engadget.com/the-legend-of-zelda-tears-of-the-kingdom-review-a-familiar-but-fresh-adventure-120035307.html"><em>The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom</em></a>.<em>&nbsp;</em>Another big Switch 2 release, <a href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/nintendo/donkey-kong-bananza-hands-on-a-funky-fresh-take-on-nintendos-favorite-ape-130057272.html"><em>Donkey Kong Bananza</em></a><em>, </em>will be available shortly starting on July 17 but is still up for pre-order now.</p> \n<p>As of this publication, just about all Switch 2 games are broadly available. Stock for the accessories remains a little spottier, but most devices are still available at multiple retailers. <a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ffe106af-8248-4af3-9098-a2d4fd637766&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=9bc3966d-0466-4076-9841-6bc2e9920c17&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GameStop&amp;linkText=Nintendo%27s+official+Switch+2+carrying+cases&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASr0vgzpdHdX6jfYLRkY_a8IHoDe8DOXsoVL4u5O51Uo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fgaming-accessories%2Fcases-stands%2Fnintendo-switch-2%2Fproducts%2Fnintendo-switch-2-all-in-one-carrying-case%2F20021981.html">Nintendo's official Switch 2 carrying cases</a> have been the main exceptions, so you may need to look to third-party alternatives if you want some protection for your console right away.</p> \n<p><strong><em>Mario Kart World </em></strong><strong>($80)</strong></p> \n<ul> \n <li><p><a href="https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/mario-kart-world-switch-2/">Nintendo</a></p></li> \n <li><p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;itemId=walmart_transaction_15940407280&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=9bc3966d-0466-4076-9841-6bc2e9920c17&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;linkText=Walmart&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAT2D8dQVwyjo2c3zPpt3ni5EtDqvP4yLlVnPH-c2FkhV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FMario-Kart-World-U-S-Version%2F15940407280">Walmart</a></p></li> \n <li><p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ffe106af-8248-4af3-9098-a2d4fd637766&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;contentUuid=9bc3966d-0466-4076-9841-6bc2e9920c17&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GameStop&amp;linkText=GameStop&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUbgZzeKp0N4jagFMgc1eggbGH4k1HJ5ftHxZV8CiEwQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fvideo-games%2Fnintendo-switch-2%2Fproducts%2Fmario-kart-world---nintendo-switch-2%2F20021637.html">GameStop</a></p></li> \n <li><p><a class="rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&a